      "Panel C depicts the joint predicted log(OR) surface across the ",
      "5th-95th percentile range of both exposures; ",
      "contour lines indicate OR thresholds of 1.00 (white dashed), ",
      "1.20 (gold solid), and 1.50 (magenta solid). ",
      "Note: predicted OR values in this cohort range from 0.98 to 4.68; ",
      "no region falls below OR=1.00 at the population median reference. ",
      "Grey areas represent regions with insufficient data for stable estimation. ",
